<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:13:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于中国和美国电动汽车的增长，今年汽油需求增长将放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gasoline-demand-growth-slow-this-year-ev-growth-china-us-2024-05-06/</link><description>分析师表示，受中国和美国转向电动汽车以及去年 COVID-19 疫情爆发后恢复正常消费的推动，全球汽油需求增长可能会在 2024 年减半，从而挤压下半年炼油厂的利润率。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:23:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gasoline-demand-growth-slow-this-year-ev-growth-china-us-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾表示不会加剧南海紧张局势，不会使用高压水枪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-wont-raise-south-china-sea-tensions-wont-use-water-cannons-2024-05-06/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，该国不会在南海使用高压水枪或任何进攻性武器。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:20:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-wont-raise-south-china-sea-tensions-wont-use-water-cannons-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>美联储削减押注，亚洲股市上涨；日元回落涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-06/</link><description>由于市场重新押注美联储今年可能会降息，亚洲股市周一上涨，而日元在上周因东京疑似货币干预而大幅上涨后走软。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示，4月份中国服务业活动有所放缓，但仍保持稳健</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-eases-april-still-solid-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-05-06/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，由于成本上升，中国服务业活动扩张略有放缓，但新订单增长加速，商业信心稳步上升，提振了经济持续复苏的希望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 01:53:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-eases-april-still-solid-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国就业报告疲软后美元持稳；日元本周开局不利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-after-soft-us-jobs-report-yen-starts-week-back-foot-2024-05-06/</link><description>美元周一大体持稳，因疲软的美国就业报告提振了美联储今年仍可能降息两次的押注，而日元本周初小幅走软。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 01:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-after-soft-us-jobs-report-yen-starts-week-back-foot-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：金融状况亮起绿灯，外汇平静</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 21:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>库尔最后时刻的进球为中央海岸赢得了亚足联杯决赛的胜利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/late-kuol-strike-earns-central-coast-victory-final-afc-cup-2024-05-05/</link><description>周日，中央海岸水手队在马斯喀特苏丹卡布斯体育场以 1-0 战胜黎巴嫩阿尔阿赫德队，成为第一支赢得亚足联杯冠军的澳大利亚俱乐部。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 18:45:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/late-kuol-strike-earns-central-coast-victory-final-afc-cup-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国队击败印度尼西亚队夺得汤姆斯杯和尤伯杯双冠王</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/china-down-indonesia-claim-thomas-uber-cup-double-2024-05-05/</link><description>中国男队在周日的两项比赛中夺得尤伯杯冠军，印尼队获得亚军，时隔六年后，中国男队重新夺回汤姆斯杯冠军。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 15:38:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/china-down-indonesia-claim-thomas-uber-cup-double-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔哈撒韦公司的布鲁克斯跑步首席执行官将中国和欧洲视为增长领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/berkshires-brooks-running-ceo-sees-china-europe-growth-areas-2024-05-05/</link><description>布鲁克斯跑步公司的新任首席执行官表示，这家由沃伦·巴菲特旗下的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司拥有的跑鞋制造商将中国和欧洲视为该公司在美国创收最多的业务的增长领域</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 10:10:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/berkshires-brooks-running-ceo-sees-china-europe-growth-areas-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>马克龙准备谈贸易之际，中国习近平赞扬法国关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/frances-macron-set-press-visiting-xi-trade-ukraine-2024-05-05/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平周日抵达巴黎，在与欧盟贸易争端日益加剧的背景下进行罕见访问，称赞中法关系是国际典范。</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 00:03:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/frances-macron-set-press-visiting-xi-trade-ukraine-2024-05-05/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔股东拒绝气候、多元化、中国提案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/berkshire-shareholders-reject-climate-diversity-china-proposals-2024-05-04/</link><description>周六，伯克希尔哈撒韦公司股东以压倒性多数否决了沃伦·巴菲特集团解决环境和社会政策问题的六项提案，这位亿万富翁投资者及其董事会都反对所有这些提案。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 21:52:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/berkshire-shareholders-reject-climate-diversity-china-proposals-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>法国化妆品行业期待习近平访华以缓和中国进口规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-cosmetics-sector-eyes-xi-visit-reprieve-chinese-import-rules-2024-05-04/</link><description>法国世界领先的化妆品行业指望习近平和马克龙下周举行会谈，以帮助最大限度地减少中国严格的新进口规则要求分享配方和制造技术对法国公司的影响。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 10:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-cosmetics-sector-eyes-xi-visit-reprieve-chinese-import-rules-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>前任命者表示，如果特朗普获胜，台湾将得到特朗普的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-will-have-trumps-support-if-he-wins-ex-appointee-says-2024-05-04/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普任命的一位前美国大使周六表示，他相信这位前总统如果重新入主白宫，将再次支持台湾。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 09:58:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-will-have-trumps-support-if-he-wins-ex-appointee-says-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>瑞信中国证券合资公司称2023年员工人数将减少46%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-suisse-china-securities-jv-says-staff-down-46-2023-2024-05-04/</link><description>瑞士信贷在中国的证券经纪合资企业表示，2023 年其员工人数将减少 46%，这一年瑞士当局安排了一次收购，以防止该公司倒闭。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 08:05:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-suisse-china-securities-jv-says-staff-down-46-2023-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>印度外交部长拒绝拜登的“仇外”言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-foreign-minister-rejects-bidens-xenophobia-comment-2024-05-04/</link><description>据《经济时报》周六报道，印度外交部长苏杰生驳斥了美国总统乔·拜登有关“仇外心理”阻碍印度经济增长的言论。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 05:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-foreign-minister-rejects-bidens-xenophobia-comment-2024-05-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>